#: ../src/docs/guides/proxies/pound.md:125
#, no-wrap
msgid "The \"ListenHTTP\" section represents the service `http` (Port 80) and the \"Address\" that the proxy will listen on. We will change this to the actual IP of our Pound server.\n"
msgstr ""

