msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/guides/proxies/pound.md:457
#, no-wrap
msgid "There are a *LOT* of options that can be included in your `pound.conf` file, including error message directives, logging options, time out values, etc. You can find more on what is available by [looking here.](https://linux.die.net/man/8/pound)\n"
