#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/guides/proxies/pound.md:459
#, no-wrap
msgid "Conveniently, Pound automatically figures out if one of the \"BackEnd\" servers is off-line and disables it so that web services can continue without delay. It also automatically sees them again when they are back on-line.\n"
