#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/guides/proxies/pound.md:463
#, no-wrap
msgid "Pound offers another option for those who do not want to use HAProxy or Nginx as for load balancing. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/guides/proxies/pound.md:465
#, no-wrap
msgid "Pound as a load balancing server is very easy to install, set up and use. As noted here, Pound can also be used as a reverse proxy, and there are a lot of proxy and load balancing options available. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/guides/proxies/pound.md:466
#, no-wrap
msgid "And you should always remember to keep security in mind when setting up any service, including a load-balancing proxy server.\n"
